data.text:
More information on Gabriella Wilde can be found here. Actress who gained fame as a model and has acted in the 2011 movie The Three Musketeers and in the 2013 remake of Carrie. LONDON, ENGLAND – FEBRUARY 18: (L-R) Tom Hooper, Douglas Booth, Gabriella Wilde in the front row of the Burberry Prorsum Autumn Winter 2013 Womenswear show on Februin London, England. Gabriella Wilde has 3 siblingsin Her family: Isabella Calthorpe, Olivia Llewellyn, Arabella Llewellyn. Wilde has modeled for labels like Abercrombie & Fitch, Topshop, Lacoste, Estée Lauder, and Burberry. Discovered at 14 by Naomi Campbell after the modeling icon spotted her at a dinner party, Ms.

(Photo: GLYN KIRK/AFP/Getty Images) She Has Modeled For Big-Name Brands She studied fine art at the City and Guilds of London Art School but dropped out to pursue acting. Wilde told the Daily Mail, “and although we’re not officially stepsisters, she was my best friend when we were little and we grew up together, so she kind of is anyway.” Siblings: Isabella Calthorpe, Olivia Llewellyn, Arabella Llewellyn, Octavia Elsa, Georgiana Moireach Gay, Jacobi Richard Penn Gabriella Wilde Education She attended Heathfield St Mary’s School, Ascot, and St Swithun’s School, Winchester.
